         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">10/10/77 ¶ On board of the "Siam" ¶  ¶ I write a few lines on the mail steamer, dear Mr Bentham, now near King George's Sound, ¶ WA. ¶  ¶ where we will land to morrow. I suddenly resolved to embark, a...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">77.10.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Kew Correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1871-81,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>f. 203.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10/10/77</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">On board of the "Siam"</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I write a few lines on the mail steamer, dear Mr Bentham, now near King George's Sound,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>WA.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>where we will land to morrow. I suddenly resolved to embark, as my health had given way and as I was mentally so oppressed, altho my worldly affairs do not admit of much itineration.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>G.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Berry, 26 September 1877. M left Melbourne on 4 October 1877 (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>, 5 October 1877,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p. 4).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is my intention to get within the few weeks —allotted to my absense — so far as Shark Bay, to see how far there the southern &amp; the tropical forms of plants are meeting. Novelty can hardly be expected there. I shall just be in time for the late spring-vegetation &amp; the early summer-flowers.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The mail steamer with the European post has met us yesterday; so I shall not likely get any letters or prints from you, until December, when I hope to be again at Albany.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>WA.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall be much<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>interested in your and General<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Munro's views about our Australian grasses.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>William Munro.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is wonderful, that your eyesight, after half a century's work, remains so faithful to you, for appreciating even the minute analytic details of grasses.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I envey Sir J. Hooker for his splendid journey with Asa Gray to Arizona, Utah &amp; New Mexico.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For descriptions of Joseph Hooker's journey see Allan (1967),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pp. 231-2, and Desmond (1999), pp. 248–50.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me hope, that your health remains firm.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardful yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
